---
import Divider from "../../common/Divider.astro";
---

<Divider caseStudies={true} />
<section class="container py-[40px] md:py-[64px]">
  <div class="grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <h2
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] font-light uppercase triangle-text-after text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      Executive Summary
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[24px] md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[18px] md:text-[22px] leading-[1.5] text-white/80">
        I rebuilt icebaths.com end to end. I inherited a broken, unfinished Shopify
        store that Google hadn't even indexed, with zero acquisition tactics in
        place. I migrated the brand across three platforms, designed every page in
        Figma, art-directed the lifestyle and product shoots, and built the
        marketing engine behind it.
      </p>
      <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[18px] md:text-[22px] leading-[1.5] text-white">
        In the first four months after launch, the site went from invisible to
        54.8k impressions, 1,210 clicks, and 139 qualified leads — an 11.5%
        click-to-lead conversion rate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
